section.text:
It is the sense of Congress that the President should greatly expand the list of 18 Russian officials and others published on April 12, 2013, who were engaged in actions described in 
            section 404 of the Sergei Magnitsky Rule of Law Accountability Act of 2012 (title IV of 
            Public Law 112–208
          ; 
            22 U.S.C. 5811

          ) regarding the death of Sergei Magnitsky, illegal activity by officials of the Government of the Russian Federation, or violations of human rights and other offenses in Russia.
